
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Rating";
}
<section class="section header-section dark">
    <div class="overlay"><img class="property-cover" src="/images/bg1.jpg"></div>
    <div class="container clearfix">
        <div class="col-lg-6 centered aligncenter">
            <div class="centralizing-wrapper">
                <div class="centralized-content">
                    <h1>Don't just visit. <span style="color:#f06eaa">Belong.</span></h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="section2 bordered">
    <div class="container clearfix">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                <h2>Velvett Homestays – <span class="vh-pink-txt">The Pink Awards</span></h2>
                <div class="head-underline-s"> </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">

                <p>In appreciation of the hard work and efforts our home owners make to maintain their homestays for the comfort of all our clients we at Velvett Homestays have created The Pink Awards.</p>

                <p>The Pink Awards categorise the level of excellence the property maintains and customer satisfaction received at each individual homestay.</p>

                <p>
                    We have carefully selected symbols which self-represent the level of commendation for each homestay and are a step further ahead from the norm of star ratings.
                    Whilst all our properties are handpicked and personally viewed to guarantee a perfect homestay experience we acknowledge that no two places are the same and may vary in location, style and additional extras.
                </p>

                <p><br></p>
                <hr>
                <h4 class="vh-pink-txt">The Pink Butterfly Award</h4>
                <p><img src="/images/butterfly.png" alt=""></p>
                <p>
                    The attractive, colourful and eye catching butterfly represents our properties which offer you a good standard of homestay excellence and customer satisfaction.
                    These modern and stylish properties are guaranteed to satisfy, they are fully equipped and meet our expectations for a pleasant homestay.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>
                <hr>
                <h4 class="vh-pink-txt">The Pink Deer Award</h4>
                <p><img src="/images/deer.png" alt=""></p>
                <p>
                    This graceful, elegant and yet independently charming deer represents our properties which offer a high standard of excellence and customer satisfaction.
                    These properties are guaranteed to make you feel at home the moment you step through the doors, your level of homestay comfort will be exceptional and welcoming.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>
                <hr>
                <h4 class="vh-pink-txt">The Pink Eagle Award</h4>
                <p><img src="/images/eagle.png" alt=""></p>
                <p>
                    This soaring bird in flight, with a sharp eye and awe inspiring wing span represents our properties which are a cut above the rest in terms of homestay excellence and customer satisfaction.
                    These properties guarantee a level of homestay luxury that is incomparable, sophisticated and decadent.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>
                <p><br></p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>